hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: I've been made redundant washing machine motion sensor A-Rod is said to be resting that sore quad that prevented him from joining the Yankees in Texas this week, all the while painting himself as the victim in all of this to anyone who will listen. He wants everyone to believe that it is the Yankees who are going out of their way to keep him off the field, even though he was the one who brought up the quad issue last week.
